Definition: mathematics) a miscalculation that results from rounding off numbers to a convenient number of decimals
Example: the error in the calculation was attributable to rounding; taxes are rounded off to the nearest dollar but the rounding error is surprisingly small
Synonyms: rounding_error, miscalculation, noun, cognition, math, c, mathematics, a, that, results, from, off, numbers, to, convenient, number, of, decimals, the, error, in, calculation, was, attributable, taxes, are, rounded, nearest, dollar, but, is, surprisingly, small
Category: noun.act
